headline: Wall Street, crypto industry say tokenization will reshape global markets: 'It’s going to eat the entire financial system'
summary: The crypto industry, along with Wall Street heavyweights, wants to bring tokenized stocks, or digital versions of traditional shares that are recorded on a blockchain's digital ledger, into the mainstream.
